+# Junie Translator Project
+
+A Python program for translating SRT subtitle files using AI services.
+
+## Features
+
+- Translate SRT subtitle files to any language using AI services
+- Process one line at a time for accurate translations
+- Display a progress bar showing translation progress
+- Support for different translation services (OpenAI, DeepSeek, etc.)
+- Customizable AI prompts for different translation styles
+
+## Installation
+
+This project uses [uv](https://github.com/astral-sh/uv) for package management.
+
+```bash
+# Clone the repository
+git clone https://github.com/yourusername/junie-translator-project.git
+cd junie-translator-project
+
+# Install the package
+uv pip install .
+```
+
+## Configuration
+
+### Basic Configuration (config.json)
+
+Create a `config.json` file in your project directory:
+
+```json
+{
+  "from-language": "auto",
+  "to-language": "Spanish",
+  "ai-api-service": {
+    "api-service-provider": "openai",
+    "api-key": "your-api-key-here"
+  },
+  "output-directory": "./output",
+  "model": "gpt-3.5-turbo"
+}
+```
+
+Key options:
+- `from-language`: Source language ("auto" for automatic detection)
+- `to-language`: Target language (required)
+- `ai-api-service`: AI service provider configuration
+- `model`: AI model to use
+
+### AI Provider Configuration (aiprovider.json)
+
+The project includes an `aiprovider.json` file that configures different AI providers (OpenAI, DeepSeek, etc.).
+
+## Usage
+
+### Command Line
+
+```bash
+# Use default config.json in current directory
+srt-translate
+
+# Specify a custom config file
+srt-translate -c my-config.json
+```
+
+### Environment Variables
+
+```bash
+export OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key
+export DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=your-deepseek-api-key
+```
+
+### Python API
+
+```python
+from junie_translator_project.main import translate_srt
+
+# Basic usage
+output_path = translate_srt(
+    input_path="input.srt",
+    target_language="Spanish"
+)
+```
+
